cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper is about a shared task on fact extraction and verification, which involves natural language processing and machine learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which deals with the intersection of computer science and linguistics. The paper also involves the use of artificial intelligence and machine learning, which makes cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) a likely sub-category as well. The task also involves classification, which falls under cs.LG (Learning), and information retrieval, which falls under cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, some of the participating systems may have used neural networks, which falls under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
